OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773684358
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FTwo students from Kent have died,
OL,7,Fwhile several more are in hospital,
OL,8,Fafter an outbreak of meningitis in the
OL,9,FCanterbury area.
OL,11,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,12,Fhas said the outbreak is likely to be
OL,13,Fmeningococcal, caused by the bacterium
OL,14,FNeisseria meningitidis.
OL,16,FSome students at the University of
OL,17,FKent have been given antibiotics while
OL,18,Fothers are in hospital. The specific
OL,19,Fstrain of meningitis has not yet been
OL,20,Fidentified.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
